NuLife Sciences, Inc. Key Developments

NuLife Sciences, Inc. Appoints John Hollister as Chief Executive Officer
May 18 17
On May 15, 2017, the Board of Directors of NuLife Sciences, Inc. appointed John Hollister as the company's Chief Executive Officer. John Hollister, age 56. Chief Executive Officer. In addition to his role as Chief Executive Officer of the Company, Since September 2015, Mr. Hollister has served as the acting Chief Executive Officer of Northsight Capital, Inc., Previously, from May 2014 to August 2015, Mr. Hollister served as Chief Executive Officer and Director of NEMUS Bioscience, Inc.


NuLife Sciences, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 15 17
On 05/15/2017, NuLife Sciences, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


